| ColumnHandling-A-002-M | Format    | Column Handling | MUST       | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Column IDs MUST use Pascal case.                                                                                                                                                          | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-003-M | Format    | Column Handling | MUST NOT   | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Column IDs MUST NOT use abbreviations.                                                                                                                                                    | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-004-M | Format    | Column Handling | MUST       | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Column IDs MUST be alphanumeric with no special characters.                                                                                                                               | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-005-O | Format    | Column Handling | SHOULD NOT | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Column IDs SHOULD NOT use acronyms.                                                                                                                                                       | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-006-O | Format    | Column Handling | SHOULD NOT | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Column IDs SHOULD NOT exceed 50 characters to accommodate column length restrictions of various data repositories.                                                                        | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-007-M | Format    | Column Handling | MUST       | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Columns that have an ID and a Name MUST have the `Id` or `Name` suffix in the Column ID.                                                                                                  | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-008-C | Format    | Column Handling | MAY        | All Rows              | if there are no other columns with the same name prefix | Column display names MAY avoid the `Name` suffix if there are no other columns with the same name prefix.                                                                                 | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-009-M | Format    | Column Handling | MUST       | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Columns with the `Category` suffix MUST be normalized.                                                                                                                                    | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-010-M | Composite | Column Handling | MUST       | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Custom (e.g., provider-defined) columns that are not defined by FOCUS but included in a *FOCUS dataset* MUST follow the following rules:                                                  | AND(ColumnHandling-A-011-M, ColumnHandling-A-012-O)                                                                                                                                                 | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-011-M | Format    | Column Handling | MUST       | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Custom columns MUST be prefixed with a consistent `x_` prefix to identify them as external, custom columns and distinguish them from FOCUS columns to avoid conflicts in future releases. | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-012-O | Format    | Column Handling | SHOULD     | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Custom columns SHOULD follow the same rules listed above for FOCUS columns.                                                                                                               | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
