| ColumnHandling-A-014-O | Order     | Column Handling | SHOULD     | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | All FOCUS columns SHOULD be first in the provided dataset.                                                                                                                                | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-015-O | Order     | Column Handling | SHOULD     | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Custom columns SHOULD be listed after all FOCUS columns.                                                                                                                                  | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-016-O | Order     | Column Handling | SHOULD NOT | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Custom columns SHOULD NOT be intermixed.                                                                                                                                                  | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-017-O | Order     | Column Handling | MAY        | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Columns MAY be sorted alphabetically.                                                                                                                                                     | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-018-O | Order     | Column Handling | SHOULD     | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Custom columns SHOULD be after all FOCUS columns.                                                                                                                                         | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
| ColumnHandling-A-019-M | Format    | Column Handling | MUST       | All Rows              | All Rows                                                | Exceptions: Identifiers will use the "Id" abbreviation since this is a standard pattern across the industry.                                                                              | null                                                                                                                                                                                                | static | 1.2                 | active | —              |
